{"tid":2139641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BBC - TikTok抖音之外 特朗普還將封禁什麼？","createTime":"2020-08-04T12:08:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T12:22:21.000Z","uid":179729,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b60819fa2715f5b30130a6ab4b8dcbe4ba3da87","tid":2139641,"uid":179729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">全文：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53648979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53648979&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=363edfa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53648979&h=704d5b85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53648979</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普週一（8月3日）稱，如果TikTok未能在9月15日前完成出售，將在美國遭封禁。而中國其他的應用軟件和服務可能也會成為目標。<br />\n<br />\n週日（8月2日），美國國務卿蓬佩奧稱，一些亞洲國家的科技公司正在&ldquo;直接向中國共產黨提供數據&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n其他哪些中國應用程序也面臨風險？最明顯的是騰訊的微信，這是除了TikTok之外，蓬佩奧點名的唯一產品。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/posts/3749368938413082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbcnewstrad%2Fposts%2F3749368938413082&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd2a%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=80e9ba4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bbcnewstrad/posts/3749368938413082</a>"},{"pid":"88baaa109075f1f016845d32776615c60903ddec","tid":2139641,"uid":261796,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"封撚哂D軟件就岩架啦"},{"pid":"4ef59c857a86861f8083bee295e09cbed4f9e37e","tid":2139641,"uid":242805,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T12:09:18.000Z","msg":"微信<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c7d0b18af97e25c9cd